Name: Maidesktop
About the game: A cute maid joins the desktop of your computer. You can get more costumes and motions through interacting with her. You punish the maid for not doing her job well. *Realistic physics are applied to the head, chest and buttocks. *A charming maid lives autonomously on the desktop without burdening the cpu. *The game offers a great variety of options for your convenience. *Her gaze responds to your mouse movements. Do not hit the change button continuously. The object may disappear.
